Sorry about the re-post, I accidentily compiled the wrong version. I tried to delete the other one, but it wont let me. So here is the right version. Sorry for double posting and any inconveniance this may cause.



===PLOT===

Terrorists have stolen two nuclear warheads and taken camp in an abandoned cold war munitions store. They plan to arm and detonate the nukes unless the Counter-terrorism team can stop them.

---Thank You---

I would like to thank Stefan Wimmreuter for all the modeling work he did for this map you can check out his work at www.StefW.com. He created the metal towers, ibeams, ibeam mounts, and the missile that is in bomb site B. Another thanks to JC-Modern for making the missile that is in bomb site A. I would also like to thank everyone that helped in both alpha tests. A big thanks to CPL|Chris and Mike Sek (Game Manager of CAL) for helping me get this map ready for a beta. And the biggest thanks of all to n@rby, the original creator of this map. (I was not able to reach n@rby in order to receive permission, but I give all credit to the layout and design of the map to him, if anyone knows his e-mail and can pass it along to me that would be great, but as of now I still have not heard back from him)

===Creator's Notes===

This map is a re-make of de_comrade_3rdroute which was a CAL map in 1.6 for a while. This map is undergoing testing by the CPL and CAL to hopefully become a new CPL/CAL map. This map has been in the works for around 3 months now and has undergone many changes to get to this point. One thing, many of you that have played comrade before will notice right off that bat is the extra route. This extra route should hopefully provide a well needed balance to the map. This map may still undergo route changes and other things based on how the CPL/CAL testing goes. This map is almost entirely custom textures.

===Issues===

There are a few issues that I am aware of that are problems with the map right now, such as no sound and no area names. Those are all things that will be in the final version. I also am aware that the overview is messed up, no clue why it looks the way it does, but I will fix it.

If you notice any other bugs and or problems e-mail me at hunch514@gmail.com

A Small packaging company has been used to smuggle government biological weapons, in order to sell on to highest bidding countries.

Bomb Target B:
Bombing the records office, so that the terrorists can steal the weapons and remove any trace of them, so that they can be used on the government which means to sell them.

Included is:
A custom nav

DE_COLDHAZE: The place where you freeze and die! 

STORYLINE (I made this one up!): Terrorism still goes on and then, the Arctic Terrorists, with the help of the 3 Terrorists group, went to a village located at the northern part of Canada to salvage things and destroy. They're planning to plant a bomb near the pension house and at a house near the hiking grounds in order to start an avalanche. 

TERRORISTS: Plant the bomb to start the avalanche or eliminate any hostile in the area. 
COUNTER-TERRORISTS: Eliminate the terrorists and stop them from planting the bomb. 

GET YOUR JACKETS BECAUSE THE REAL FROSTBITE STARTS NOW! 

17Buddies.net 

============= 

NOTE: If there are errors in this map, I can't fix them.

This is my second map, which is a remake of my first map de_siberia_final.  I felt that siberia had a lot of potential, so i have updated the look from scratch and also expanded all areas.
Hope you like it.

Note: Certain areas can be a little bit dark, so just have to up the gamma a little and should be fine.

This is the final version. I have changed a few minor bugs but from all the good feedback I haven't really had to change anything huge :)

----I have lightened the images so that you can see them better! :D The areas are a lot more "visible" in-game.. its just the interference (browser scrollbar and light things on the webpage) around the image that makes them harder to see.  While the screenshots may not look "real scary"... it is the sounds, the black fog that everything fades into at a distance and the ambiance (heavy rain and urban setting) that really makes this map as scary as it is.  It is FULL of custom sounds (from silent hill / sounddogs / resident evil / and other games).----

STORY:

A strange, thick, dark fog falls over the little town of Lugnut Arizona.
Moans can be heard in the distance. Screams from people being killed fill the air. But this is NOT why the Counter-Terrorist team has been called into this nightmarish town. The reason they have been called to this town is because a group of unknown terrorists have entered the city and are going to attempt to blow up one of the barricades set up by the civilians of Lugnut, or blow up the old lumber mill. Either one will open a way for the zombies to enter the "secure" sector of the city and kill all the remaining survivors...


*NOTE*: Be sure not to adjust your brightness or gamma, but turn down the lights in your room when you travel to Lugnut Arizona (the map...) :P LOL. This is a dark map best played in the DARK :D *cue evil laugh*
